Ses taches rondes mettent de
llectricit. Il senroule autour
de ses proies et les lectrocute.

They coil around foes and shock them
with electricity-generating organs that
seem simply to be circular patterns.

Un Pokmon dot dun gros apptit. Il
paralyse ses proies avec des dcharges
lectriques avant de les manger.

These Pokmon have a big appetite.
When they spot their prey, they attack
it and paralyze it with electricity.

It wraps itself around its prey and
paralyzes it with electricity from the
round spots on its sides. Then it chomps.

Schlingt sich um Gegner, lhmt sie ber die rund

Se enrolla alrededor de su presa, la paraliza con la
electricidad de sus marcas circulares y le asesta
mordiscos.

Si avvinghia alla preda e la paralizza rilasciando
elettricit dalle macchie tonde, poi la ingoia intera.
